Package: moneca
Title: Mobility Network Clustering Analysis
Description: moneca creates a weighted network from a mobility table and uses cliques (or similar) to create discrete and nested clusters. This is a maintained fork of the original MONECA package with modernized visualizations, comprehensive testing, and enhanced documentation.
URL: https://github.com/gmontaletti/moneca
Version: 0.5.4
Maintainer: Giampaolo Montaletti <giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com>
